title: The Complete Ida Family Guy Timeline

media:group.media:title: The Complete Ida Family Guy Timeline
media:group.media:description:
In this video we look at the entire evolution of Ida Davis from Family Guy. Voiced by seth macfarlane, we look at Ida's entire life history, her past and future. Taking a look at the Family Guy cutaways, as well as the full Family Guy episodes, I've put Ida's life in chronological order. From season 1 to newest Family Guy season.
I go into Ida and Quagmire's relationship, as well as her romance with Brian.

We also look at the funniest Family Guy moments from Peter, Lois, Chris, Meg and Brian. As well as other Family Guy characters from Quahog Rhode Island.
